  • Constructor Details

    • BloodBagReport

      public BloodBagReport​(long total, long available, long used, long transfered, long dropped, long apos, long aneg, long bpos, long bneg, long ZEROpos, long ZEROneg, long ABpos, long ABneg, long usedThisWeek, long expiredThisWeek)
      Constructor method of the BloodBagReport class
      Parameters:
      total - total of the bags of the report
      available - how many bags are available
      used - how many bags have been used
      transfered - how many bags have been transferred
      dropped - how many bags were thrown
      apos - how many pockets of A + there are
      aneg - how many pockets of A- are there
      bpos - how many pockets of B + there are
      bneg - how many pockets of B- are there
      ZEROpos - how many pockets of 0+ there are
      ZEROneg - how many pockets of 0- are there
      ABpos - how many pockets of AB + there are
      ABneg - how many pockets of AB- are there
      usedThisWeek - how many bags have been used this weekend
      expiredThisWeek - how many bags are expiring this weekend
